#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:107 b50e2c2b227a431296da568d63d0183a
msgid ""
"The dispatch is **by name, not by position** — ``forward(self, u, v)`` and "
"``forward(self, v, u)`` are equivalent. The contract only fails if you use "
"an unrecognised name; you will get a clear ``ValueError`` at call time "
"pointing to the bad argument."
msgstr ""
"分派是 **按名称而非按位置** 进行的——``forward(self, u, v)`` 和 ``forward(self, v, u)`` "
"是等价的。只有当你使用了无法识别的名称时约定才会失败；此时你会在调用时收到一个清晰的 ``ValueError``\\ ，指出出错的参数。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:114 bc05b3cddf264650b82352f696324955
msgid ""
"You never call ``forward`` yourself. The library calls it under ``vmap`` for"
" every quadrature point of every element, so even a trivial ``print(u)`` "
"inside ``forward`` will fire :math:`N_e \\times N_q` times and produce "
"strange-looking traced tensors. For debugging weak forms, set "
"``batch_size=1`` and call the assembler on a one-element mesh, or check the "
"assembled output directly with ``K.to_dense()``."
msgstr ""
"你永远不需要自己调用 ``forward``\\ 。库会在 ``vmap`` 下针对每个单元的每个求积点调用它，因此即便是在 ``forward`` "
"中写一个简单的 ``print(u)``\\ ，也会触发 :math:`N_e \\times N_q` "
"次，并打印出看起来很奇怪的被追踪张量。调试弱形式时，请设置 ``batch_size=1`` 并在仅含一个单元的网格上调用装配器，或直接用 "
"``K.to_dense()`` 检查装配结果。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:126 dfad6d2f409644c69aabd9f3be96fc4e
msgid "ElementAssembler — bilinear forms"
msgstr "ElementAssembler——双线性形式"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:128 2e2ae0492e744f44bbb196be37fec8a4
msgid ""
"For ``a(u, v)``, write a ``forward(...)`` that returns the integrand and "
"call ``from_mesh(...)`` + ``()``. Calling the assembler returns a "
":class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix`."
msgstr ""
"对于 ``a(u, v)``\\ ，编写一个返回被积函数的 ``forward(...)``\\ ，然后调用 ``from_mesh(...)`` + "
"``()``\\ 。调用装配器会返回一个 :class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:146 1e275c0081054a67bd1ff2b2e0bd4c1b
msgid ""
"That's the whole user story for a scalar bilinear form: one ``forward`` "
"method, three lines of glue, sparse matrix in hand."
msgstr "对于标量双线性形式，整个用户流程就这么简单：一个 ``forward`` 方法、三行胶水代码，稀疏矩阵到手。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:149 f37c5c1fbd08440c96fbd23898c6a140
msgid "The full call signature is"
msgstr "完整的调用签名为"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:156 fb39318b6f6a4954b8fb566a2353e030
msgid ""
"with all arguments optional. The mesh's own ``points`` are used when "
"``points=None``; ``func`` lets you swap in a different integrand without "
"defining a new subclass (handy in inverse problems where the bilinear form "
"is a moving target); the three ``*_data`` dicts plumb call-time inputs into "
"your ``forward`` parameters (see :ref:`forms-data-plumbing`); ``batch_size``"
" is a memory knob covered in :ref:`forms-batching`."
msgstr ""
"其中所有参数都是可选的。当 ``points=None`` 时使用网格自身的 ``points``\\ ；\\ ``func`` "
"让你无需定义新子类即可替换为不同的被积函数（在双线性形式不断变化的反问题中很方便）；三个 ``*_data`` 字典把调用期输入传递给你的 "
"``forward`` 参数（参见 :ref:`forms-data-plumbing`\\ ）；\\ ``batch_size`` "
"是一个内存控制旋钮，详见 :ref:`forms-batching`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:166 d644017259054aa09c801102505cf37d
msgid ""
"Parameters that vary by mesh: ``point_data``, ``element_data``, "
"``scalar_data``"
msgstr "随网格变化的参数：\\ ``point_data``\\ 、\\ ``element_data``\\ 、\\ ``scalar_data``"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:168 5af2da9f39eb4bba810773e70be289ce
msgid ""
"Most weak forms involve coefficients beyond just :math:`u, v, \\nabla u, "
"\\nabla v`. The three call-time dicts let you pass them in without changing "
"the assembler class itself:"
