#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:206 d942f6516f0f45318a4cf937c39a2147
msgid "Sparsity: what the assembled output actually looks like"
msgstr "稀疏性：装配输出实际长什么样"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:208 0bff7a83f9ef4630bf536b68e011d0a3
msgid ""
"The :class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix` is COO-format on top of "
"``torch_sla.SparseTensor``; you can ``@`` against it, ``.solve(b)`` against "
"it, or densify it for inspection. The two panels below show the sparsity "
"pattern of the Laplace stiffness above, next to the 2D-elasticity stiffness "
"on the *same* mesh:"
msgstr ""
":class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix` 是构建在 ``torch_sla.SparseTensor`` 之上的"
" COO 格式；你可以对它做 ``@``\\ 、对它调用 ``.solve(b)``\\ "
"，或把它转为稠密矩阵以便查看。下面两幅图展示了上述拉普拉斯刚度的稀疏模式，并与 *同一个* 网格上的二维弹性刚度并列对比："

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:214 26d20ce4597a448d9d05fe78355ab140
msgid "Stiffness sparsity, scalar Laplace vs 2D elasticity"
msgstr "刚度稀疏性：标量拉普拉斯与二维弹性的对比"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:218 81b39050c55540298e7c300c75e54352
msgid ""
"The scalar Laplace stiffness has one entry per ``(i, j)`` adjacent node "
"pair. The 2D-elasticity stiffness has the *same* connectivity but each entry"
" is now a :math:`2 \\times 2` block (one row/col per displacement "
"component), giving a matrix four times larger with sixteen times the non-"
"zeros. The library detects the block structure from the rank of your "
"``forward`` return — see the next section."
msgstr ""
"标量拉普拉斯刚度对每一对相邻节点 ``(i, j)`` 有一个条目。二维弹性刚度具有 *相同* 的连接性，但每个条目现在是一个 :math:`2 "
"\\times 2` 的分块（每个位移分量对应一行/一列），从而得到一个尺寸为四倍、非零元为十六倍的矩阵。库会根据你 ``forward`` "
"返回值的阶数自动检测这一分块结构——参见下一节。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:227 b185405ac81748a8940b481730c84189
msgid "Vector-valued forms and block-CSR output"
msgstr "向量值形式与分块 CSR 输出"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:229 daabd712a8bc4132aff2ad81e449fc45
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"For vector-valued problems (linear elasticity, Stokes velocity blocks, "
"electromagnetics in vector form) each node carries :math:`H > 1` degrees of "
"freedom. The bilinear form integrand for an entry :math:`(i, j)` is then a "
":math:`H \\times H` block, and the assembled matrix has shape "
":math:`[N_\\text{points}\\, H,\\, N_\\text{points}\\, H]`."
msgstr ""
"对于向量值问题（线弹性、斯托克斯速度分块、向量形式的电磁学），每个节点携带 :math:`H > 1` 个自由度。此时条目 :math:`(i, j)`"
" 的双线性形式被积函数是一个 :math:`H \\times H` 的分块，装配后的矩阵形状为 :math:`[N_\\text{points}\\,"
" H,\\, N_\\text{points}\\, H]`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:235 36a8922981a24ba9af16292134b8a11c
msgid ""
"The library decides scalar vs block by inspecting the *rank* of what your "
"``forward`` returns:"
msgstr "库通过检查你 ``forward`` 返回值的 *阶数* 来判断是标量还是分块："

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:238 f4fe4a1277dd4f02bf34a3d7ec7b6fba
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"``forward`` returns a 2-D tensor ``[B, B]`` → scalar, output shape "
":math:`[N_\\text{points}, N_\\text{points}]`;"
msgstr ""
"``forward`` 返回 2 维张量 ``[B, B]`` → 标量，输出形状为 :math:`[N_\\text{points}, "
"N_\\text{points}]`\\ ；"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:240 2043c3e3fc084a12856d40de76284e2f
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"``forward`` returns a 4-D tensor ``[B, B, H, H]`` → block, output shape "
":math:`[N_\\text{points}\\, H, N_\\text{points}\\, H]`."
msgstr ""
"``forward`` 返回 4 维张量 ``[B, B, H, H]`` → 分块，输出形状为 :math:`[N_\\text{points}\\,"
" H, N_\\text{points}\\, H]`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:243 63681a832e3540ce96991c01269db797
msgid "For linear elasticity in 2D, the integrand at a quadrature point is"
msgstr "对于二维线弹性，在某个求积点处的被积函数为"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:245 bed839b92b86460ba7dce9a7bc719c06
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"K_{ij}^{\\alpha\\beta} \\;=\\;\n"
"\\int_\\Omega \\mathbf{B}_i^T\\, \\mathbf{C}\\, \\mathbf{B}_j \\,\\mathrm{d}\\Omega,\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"\\mathbf{B}_i \\;=\\; \\text{Voigt}(\\nabla \\phi_i),"
msgstr ""
"K_{ij}^{\\alpha\\beta} \\;=\\;\n"
"\\int_\\Omega \\mathbf{B}_i^T\\, \\mathbf{C}\\, \\mathbf{B}_j \\,\\mathrm{d}\\Omega,\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"\\mathbf{B}_i \\;=\\; \\text{Voigt}(\\nabla \\phi_i),"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:252 35fba722582347ccacde020518c1df5e
msgid ""
"which is exactly the built-in "
":class:`~tensormesh.LinearElasticityElementAssembler`:"
msgstr "这正是内置的 :class:`~tensormesh.LinearElasticityElementAssembler`\\ ："

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:269 daf0b390d56445e6ac6223c91af60778
msgid ""
"The whole 2D mesh of 143 nodes produces a :math:`286 \\times 286` stiffness "
"— see the right panel of the figure above. Everything you read about scalar "
"problems on this page applies unchanged to block problems; only the matrix "
"shape grows."
msgstr ""
"包含 143 个节点的整个二维网格会生成一个 :math:`286 \\times 286` "
"的刚度矩阵——参见上图右侧。本页关于标量问题所讲的一切都原封不动地适用于分块问题；唯一变化的是矩阵尺寸变大了。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:278 91095a6821734a148e896672dd109d55
msgid "NodeAssembler — linear forms"
msgstr "NodeAssembler——线性形式"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:280 ae986df14e2b49f8b0d91eb12aa2cb2e
msgid ""
"For :math:`l(v)`, the same pattern but with a single basis and a vector "
"result:"
msgstr "对于 :math:`l(v)`\\ ，模式相同，但只有一个基函数，且结果为向量："

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:296 ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:369
#: 3364432044fe41b09a06fc333bcee55d bfe3e5cf500946249c47de48e3320876
msgid "Call signature:"
msgstr "调用签名："

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:303 1604dba6a0bc48b2bf346e33e1ab7226
msgid ""
"Note that ``element_data`` is *not* accepted (linear forms rarely need per-"
"element scratch data), and that the default ``batch_size`` is ``1`` rather "
"than the ``-1`` used by :class:`~tensormesh.ElementAssembler`. To disable "
"batching here pass ``batch_size=-1`` or ``batch_size=None``; see "
":ref:`forms-batching` for details."
msgstr ""
"注意这里 *不* 接受 ``element_data``\\ （线性形式很少需要逐单元的临时数据），而且默认 ``batch_size`` 为 "
"``1``\\ ，而非 :class:`~tensormesh.ElementAssembler` 所用的 ``-1``\\ "
"。若要在此处禁用分批处理，请传入 ``batch_size=-1`` 或 ``batch_size=None``\\ ；详见 :ref:`forms-"
"batching`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:309 48d02c8f7d5b4af884236ccdafde4f8f
msgid ""
"End-to-end check: combining mass + load to project a function into the FE "
"space. The mass matrix :math:`M` is SPD, so we can invert it without "
"Dirichlet conditions:"
msgstr "端到端验证：组合质量矩阵与载荷向量，把一个函数投影到有限元空间。质量矩阵 :math:`M` 是对称正定的，因此无需狄利克雷条件就能求逆："

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:313 8ce9ce7d9aed4ba4827ea13b9ae686b4
msgid "NodeAssembler load vector and L2 projection"
msgstr "NodeAssembler 载荷向量与 L2 投影"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:317 c861d073ea2445dea832331f867a8c37
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Left: the assembled load vector :math:`b_i = \\int_\\Omega f\\, \\phi_i\\, "
"\\mathrm{d}\\Omega`, plotted as colored nodal values on the mesh. Right: the"
" :math:`L^2` projection :math:`u_h = M^{-1} b`. The nodal-error magnitude of"
" ~3 × 10\\ :sup:`-3` matches the expected :math:`O(h^2)` discretisation "
"error for P1 elements on this mesh."
msgstr ""
"左图：装配得到的载荷向量 :math:`b_i = \\int_\\Omega f\\, \\phi_i\\, "
"\\mathrm{d}\\Omega`\\ ，以网格上着色的节点值形式绘制。右图：\\ :math:`L^2` 投影 :math:`u_h = "
"M^{-1} b`\\ 。约 3 × 10\\ :sup:`-3` 量级的节点误差，与该网格上 P1 单元所预期的 :math:`O(h^2)` "
"离散误差相吻合。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:323 7abed70691cf4c4588f60c4fac707e94
msgid ""
"This is the smallest possible \"weak form → assembled output → solved "
"field\" loop; the more general workflow with boundary conditions and linear-"
"solver options is the topic of :doc:`boundary_conditions` and "
":doc:`linear_solvers`."
msgstr ""
"这是“弱形式 → 装配输出 → 求解场”这一最小闭环；包含边界条件和线性求解器选项的更通用工作流，是 "
":doc:`boundary_conditions` 和 :doc:`linear_solvers` 的主题。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:328 723c50c019944138bb99964efa1f54cf
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The simplest possible load — a constant body force :math:`\\int c\\, v\\, "
"\\mathrm{d}\\Omega` — ships pre-built as "
":func:`~tensormesh.const_node_assembler`; see :ref:`forms-builtins`."
msgstr ""
"最简单的载荷——常体力 :math:`\\int c\\, v\\, \\mathrm{d}\\Omega`——已作为 "
":func:`~tensormesh.const_node_assembler` 内置提供；参见 :ref:`forms-builtins`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:336 dee861c9a864445397c2444b3b8eae87
msgid "FacetAssembler — boundary integrals"
msgstr "FacetAssembler——边界积分"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:338 d2da33ea042445c0aa9e9de2d6e44ae9
msgid ""
"For surface terms — Neumann tractions, Robin BCs, penalty contact — "
":class:`~tensormesh.FacetAssembler` runs the same dispatch over *facet* "
"quadrature instead of volume quadrature. The signature contract is identical"
" to :class:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler`'s except that the basis arguments "
"``u, v, gradu, gradv`` keep their basis dimension explicitly (1D ``[B]`` or "
"2D ``[B, D]``):"
msgstr ""
"对于面项——诺伊曼面力、罗宾边界条件、罚函数接触——:class:`~tensormesh.FacetAssembler` 在 *面* "
"数值积分（而非体数值积分）上执行相同的分派。其签名约定与 :class:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler` "
"完全一致，区别仅在于基函数参数 ``u, v, gradu, gradv`` 显式保留其基函数维度（1 维 ``[B]`` 或 2 维 ``[B, "
"D]``\\ ）："

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:358 3b553001714e4a319a716905c91563a4
msgid "Per-node boundary-integral weights on the unit square"
msgstr "单位正方形上逐节点的边界积分权重"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:363 8a287070a386429bad56ded074dc5714
msgid ""
"The assembled vector ``b`` has support only on the boundary nodes (interior "
"entries are zero). Summing all entries recovers the perimeter exactly. "
"``FacetAssembler`` defaults to integrating over ``mesh.boundary_mask``; pass"
" ``boundary_mask=...`` to ``from_mesh`` to restrict to a labelled sub-"
"boundary."
msgstr ""
"装配得到的向量 ``b`` 仅在边界节点上有支撑（内部条目为零）。对所有条目求和可精确还原出周长。\\ ``FacetAssembler`` 默认在 "
"``mesh.boundary_mask`` 上积分；向 ``from_mesh`` 传入 ``boundary_mask=...`` "
"可将其限制到带标记的子边界上。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:375 322cd13fad52455998ef4004926e9bc9
msgid ""
"(no ``element_data``, ``scalar_data``, or ``batch_size`` for facet forms.) A"
" worked penalty-contact example using "
":class:`~tensormesh.assemble.ContactAssembler` (a facet *energy* assembler) "
"lives in the :doc:`/example_gallery/index`."
msgstr ""
"（面形式不支持 ``element_data``\\ 、\\ ``scalar_data`` 或 ``batch_size``\\ 。）一个使用 "
":class:`~tensormesh.assemble.ContactAssembler`\\ （一个面 *能量* 装配器）的罚函数接触完整示例见 "
":doc:`/example_gallery/index`\\ 。"

