#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:563 9e4791e7bcef4bebaf5884a1f3f4ae07
msgid "Energy-based assemblers (``element_energy`` + ``.energy()``)"
msgstr "基于能量的装配器（\\ ``element_energy`` + ``.energy()``\\ ）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:565 a9481a6e9b164c2b90a13d0166c5fff1
msgid ""
"For nonlinear materials the most natural quantity to define is the *strain "
"energy density* :math:`\\Psi`, not the residual or stiffness:"
msgstr "对于非线性材料，最自然的定义量是 *应变能密度* :math:`\\Psi`\\ ，而非残差或刚度："

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:568 de57c918f0fc4283b7bb3d3c96757d38
msgid ""
"\\Pi(\\mathbf{u}) \\;=\\; \\int_\\Omega \\Psi(\\nabla \\mathbf{u})\\, \\mathrm{d}\\Omega,\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"\\mathbf{f}_\\text{int} \\;=\\; \\frac{\\partial \\Pi}{\\partial \\mathbf{u}},\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"\\mathbf{K}_\\text{tan} \\;=\\; \\frac{\\partial^2 \\Pi}{\\partial \\mathbf{u}^2}."
msgstr ""
"\\Pi(\\mathbf{u}) \\;=\\; \\int_\\Omega \\Psi(\\nabla \\mathbf{u})\\, \\mathrm{d}\\Omega,\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"\\mathbf{f}_\\text{int} \\;=\\; \\frac{\\partial \\Pi}{\\partial \\mathbf{u}},\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"\\mathbf{K}_\\text{tan} \\;=\\; \\frac{\\partial^2 \\Pi}{\\partial \\mathbf{u}^2}."

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:576 21035a85dc4141ac867654db98525954
msgid ""
":class:`~tensormesh.ElementAssembler` supports this pattern via a parallel "
"method, ``ElementAssembler.energy``, that integrates an ``element_energy`` "
"override and returns a scalar :class:`torch.Tensor`. Because the entire "
"pipeline is differentiable, ``E.backward()`` populates ``u.grad`` with the "
"internal force vector, and :func:`torch.autograd.functional.hessian` (or a "
"Krylov-friendly Hessian-vector product) gives the tangent stiffness:"
msgstr ""
":class:`~tensormesh.ElementAssembler` 通过一个并行方法 ``ElementAssembler.energy`` "
"支持这种模式，它会对 ``element_energy`` 重写进行积分，并返回一个标量 :class:`torch.Tensor`\\ "
"。由于整条流水线都是可微的，\\ ``E.backward()`` 会把内力向量填入 ``u.grad``\\ ，而 "
":func:`torch.autograd.functional.hessian`\\ （或一种适合 Krylov 方法的 Hessian-"
"向量积）则给出切线刚度："

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:596 66e610a193db4ecea268f1477655c10b
msgid ""
"Use the matrix-based path (``__call__`` returning a ``SparseMatrix``) for "
"*linear* and *bilinear-symmetric* problems where you already have a closed-"
"form integrand; use the energy path for hyperelasticity, plasticity, and any"
" case where autograd through the constitutive law is the cleanest expression"
" of the physics."
msgstr ""
"对于已有闭式被积函数的 *线性* 与 *双线性对称* 问题，请使用基于矩阵的路径（\\ ``__call__`` 返回 "
"``SparseMatrix``\\ ）；对于超弹性、塑性，以及任何通过对本构关系做自动微分能最简洁地表达物理的情形，请使用能量路径。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:604 b350145156c948c58af704907c08a252
msgid "A custom form: reaction-diffusion"
msgstr "一个自定义形式：反应-扩散"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:606 7f9085cfac2d422c8e6ad3d1f114b083
msgid "Combining stiffness and mass in one assembler:"
msgstr "在一个装配器中组合刚度与质量："

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:608 d4d057f9d96449c49794280e51c682bf
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"a(u, v) \\;=\\; \\int_{\\Omega} \\nabla u \\cdot \\nabla v \\;+\\; \\kappa "
"\\, u v \\, \\mathrm{d}\\Omega"
msgstr ""
"a(u, v) \\;=\\; \\int_{\\Omega} \\nabla u \\cdot \\nabla v \\;+\\; \\kappa "
"\\, u v \\, \\mathrm{d}\\Omega"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:612 04585816fcb646b4a1b96a280256d308
msgid "is just two terms inside ``forward``:"
msgstr "在 ``forward`` 内部不过是两项之和："

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:625 5c537a9b209449f5bfec53320ee7bd2b
msgid ""
"Argument order doesn't matter — the dispatch is by name. Mixing in "
"``point_data`` is just more parameters:"
msgstr "参数顺序无关紧要——分派是按名称进行的。把 ``point_data`` 混入其中也只是多几个参数而已："

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:638 9561cf785d1840dfb176cf0b5a4b191d
msgid ""
"This generalises straightforwardly: anything you can write as one algebraic "
"expression in PyTorch can go inside ``forward``, as long as the return shape"
" obeys the contract in :ref:`forms-contract`."
msgstr ""
"这一点可以直截了当地推广：只要返回形状符合 :ref:`forms-contract` 中的约定，任何你能在 PyTorch "
"中写成单一代数表达式的东西都可以放进 ``forward``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:646 3e27c7978a7d4e4d8181fa0435686387
msgid "Memory batching with ``batch_size``"
msgstr "用 ``batch_size`` 进行内存分批"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:648 6061b3798b734883b6425549cb943085
msgid ""
"For very fine meshes or high-order elements, holding all per-element "
"quadrature tensors in memory at once may not fit. The assembler ``__call__``"
" accepts a ``batch_size`` argument that splits the *quadrature* dimension "
"into chunks and accumulates the contribution:"
msgstr ""
"对于非常细的网格或高阶单元，把所有逐单元的求积张量一次性放进内存可能装不下。装配器的 ``__call__`` 接受一个 ``batch_size`` "
"参数，它把 *求积* 维度切分成若干块并逐块累加贡献："

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:657 aef10a7758da4ac2ab8a6dfa3a92bce8
msgid ""
"This is a memory knob, not problem-level vectorisation; for the latter see "
":doc:`batched_workflows`."
msgstr "这是一个内存控制旋钮，而非问题级的向量化；后者请参见 :doc:`batched_workflows`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:660 00af6cbc8d9b493399195d90973353c3
msgid "How to disable batching:"
msgstr "如何禁用分批处理："

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:662 eaef31b2d9b44fadb7c79568059c91f3
msgid ""
":class:`~tensormesh.ElementAssembler` — default ``batch_size=-1`` processes "
"all quadrature at once."
msgstr ""
":class:`~tensormesh.ElementAssembler`——默认 ``batch_size=-1``\\ ，一次性处理所有求积点。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:664 b7a972a4b4374db1a20df5b09f7d57ab
msgid ""
":class:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler` — default ``batch_size=1`` processes one "
"quadrature point at a time; pass ``-1`` or ``None`` to disable batching and "
"process all quadrature points at once."
msgstr ""
":class:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler`——默认 ``batch_size=1``\\ ，每次处理一个求积点；传入 "
"``-1`` 或 ``None`` 可禁用分批处理并一次性处理所有求积点。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:667 b0e54794c38647fcac0c855cdcd43333
msgid ""
":class:`~tensormesh.FacetAssembler` — does not expose ``batch_size``; facet "
"integrals are small enough that batching has not been needed."
msgstr ""
":class:`~tensormesh.FacetAssembler`——不暴露 ``batch_size``\\ ；面积分足够小，至今无需分批处理。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:670 05a3ffae2d4e4c0090ae9175c0ffed27
msgid ""
"Any positive integer ``batch_size`` produces the same assembled result as "
"the un-batched call. When ``batch_size`` does not evenly divide the per-"
"element quadrature count, the loop runs one extra (shorter) batch on the "
"tail; values larger than ``n_quadrature`` simply collapse to a single full "
"batch."
msgstr ""
"任何正整数 ``batch_size`` 都会得到与未分批调用相同的装配结果。当 ``batch_size`` "
"不能整除逐单元的求积点数时，循环会在末尾多跑一个（较短的）批次；大于 ``n_quadrature`` 的值则直接退化为单个完整批次。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:678 167d7d2235f94e53949da05769954ebf
msgid "Speeding up NodeAssembler with ``compile``"
msgstr "用 ``compile`` 加速 NodeAssembler"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:680 4dfa416f1a73469c943af1504ff1188a
msgid ""
":class:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler` ships a fast path that bypasses "
":func:`torch.vmap` and uses direct broadcast operations instead. Enable it "
"by chaining :meth:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler.compile`:"
msgstr ""
":class:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler` 提供了一条快速路径，它绕过 :func:`torch.vmap`\\ "
"，转而使用直接的广播运算。通过链式调用 :meth:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler.compile` 即可启用："

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:701 b5f5d4d6b1784c3592969316bf6e9d01
msgid ""
"The ``mode`` argument additionally controls whether ``torch.compile`` is "
"layered on top: ``\"disable\"`` (default) does the vmap bypass only, "
"``\"default\"`` / ``\"reduce-overhead\"`` / ``\"max-autotune\"`` enable "
"``torch.compile`` with the given level of optimisation. For most users the "
"default ``compile()`` (no ``torch.compile``) is already a large speedup with"
" no warm-up cost. :meth:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler.flat_mode` is a synonym "
"for ``compile(mode=\"disable\")``."
msgstr ""
"``mode`` 参数还控制是否在其之上叠加 ``torch.compile``\\ ：\\ ``\"disable\"``\\ （默认）只做 vmap"
" 绕过，\\ ``\"default\"`` / ``\"reduce-overhead\"`` / ``\"max-autotune\"`` "
"则以相应的优化级别启用 ``torch.compile``\\ 。对大多数用户而言，默认的 ``compile()``\\ （不含 "
"``torch.compile``\\ ）已经能带来很大的加速，且没有预热开销。\\ "
":meth:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler.flat_mode` 是 ``compile(mode=\"disable\")`` "
"的同义写法。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:709 9535558d52c2468c87987e18b772cf05
msgid ""
"The fast path only fires when **all three** of the following hold; if any of"
" them fails the call falls back transparently to the vmap path:"
msgstr "只有当以下 **三个条件全部** 满足时，快速路径才会启用；若其中任何一个不满足，调用会透明地回退到 vmap 路径："

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:712 7e22d7c0188c4678b39fe48b9eb72448
msgid ""
"``.compile()`` has been called on the assembler (``is_compiled`` returns "
"``True``)."
msgstr "已对该装配器调用过 ``.compile()``\\ （\\ ``is_compiled`` 返回 ``True``\\ ）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:714 24b599cc8a9a468c9449dd35da2dcb76
msgid ""
"The mesh has exactly one element type (``len(self.element_types) == 1``). "
"Mixed-element meshes use the vmap path even with compile enabled."
msgstr ""
"网格恰好只有一种单元类型（\\ ``len(self.element_types) == 1``\\ ）。即便启用了 compile，混合单元网格仍走 "
"vmap 路径。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:717 ba1a1950a14a492d8287037c431ae774
msgid ""
"No ``func=`` override is passed at call time. Calling ``asm(func=alt_form)``"
" always goes through the vmap path so that you can swap integrands without "
"recompiling."
msgstr ""
"调用时未传入 ``func=`` 覆盖。调用 ``asm(func=alt_form)`` 始终走 vmap "
"路径，这样你就能在不重新编译的情况下替换被积函数。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:723 fae2042a768946289891d7f25e69de75
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The fast path replaces vmap with explicit broadcast operations, which "
"imposes a stricter contract on ``forward``: it must work when ``v`` / "
"``gradv`` arrive with leading ``[n_quadrature, ...]`` / ``[n_element, "
"n_quadrature, ...]`` dimensions rather than as scalars. Closed-form forms "
"that compose those tensors via element-wise ops (``return v``, ``return "
"gradv @ vec``) work as-is; forms that index or reshape per-quadrature inputs"
" may need a few broadcast tweaks, or are simpler to leave on the default "
"vmap path. The fast path also does not auto-supply ``x``; if you need "
"coordinates, pass them in under a custom name (``point_data={\"xy\": "
"mesh.points}`` then ``forward(self, xy, v)``)."
msgstr ""
"快速路径用显式的广播运算取代 vmap，这对 ``forward`` 提出了更严格的约定：当 ``v`` / ``gradv`` 带着前导的 "
"``[n_quadrature, ...]`` / ``[n_element, n_quadrature, ...]`` "
"维度（而非以标量形式）到来时，它仍必须能正常工作。通过逐元素运算来组合这些张量的闭式形式（\\ ``return v``\\ 、\\ ``return "
"gradv @ vec``\\ ）可原样工作；而对逐求积点输入进行索引或重塑的形式可能需要一些广播上的调整，或者干脆留在默认的 vmap "
"路径上更简单。快速路径也不会自动提供 ``x``\\ ；如果你需要坐标，请用自定义名称把它传进来（\\ ``point_data={\"xy\": "
"mesh.points}``\\ ，然后 ``forward(self, xy, v)``\\ ）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:737 6e867006ff514b78a4589a86c97e876f
msgid "Writing your own assembler"
msgstr "编写你自己的装配器"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:739 16c1eec4ddbc4e958ae9c355f3d30590
msgid ""
"The library's design assumes most users will, at some point, write a custom "
"assembler. Here is the practical recipe."
msgstr "本库的设计假定大多数用户迟早都会编写自定义装配器。下面是实用的操作步骤。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:742 fbf90a91b9834411be1b941c4e3a522b
msgid ""
"**1. Pick the base class** by what you're assembling — a matrix "
"(:class:`~tensormesh.ElementAssembler`), a load vector "
"(:class:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler`), or a boundary term "
"(:class:`~tensormesh.FacetAssembler`). If the integrand is most naturally "
"expressed as a scalar energy density, use the ``.energy()`` path on "
":class:`~tensormesh.ElementAssembler` instead of writing the residual + "
"stiffness by hand — autograd will do that for you."
msgstr ""
"**1. 根据你要装配的对象挑选基类**——矩阵（\\ :class:`~tensormesh.ElementAssembler`\\ "
"）、载荷向量（\\ :class:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler`\\ ）或边界项（\\ "
":class:`~tensormesh.FacetAssembler`\\ ）。如果被积函数最自然地表示为一个标量能量密度，那么请使用 "
":class:`~tensormesh.ElementAssembler` 上的 ``.energy()`` 路径，而不要手写残差 + "
"刚度——自动微分会替你完成。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:750 700e9aec0e2343d58d99db213d0ffa63
msgid ""
"**2. Implement ``forward(self, ...)``**. Use only the parameter names listed"
" in :ref:`forms-contract` (``u``, ``v``, ``gradu``, ``gradv``, ``x``, "
"``gradx``), plus any keys you intend to pass through ``point_data``, "
"``element_data``, ``scalar_data``. Return the per-point integrand at the "
"right rank: scalar problems return ``[B, B]`` (Element) or ``[B]`` (Node / "
"Facet); block problems return ``[B, B, H, H]`` or ``[B, H]``."
msgstr ""
"**2. 实现 ``forward(self, ...)``**\\ 。只使用 :ref:`forms-contract` 中列出的参数名（\\ "
"``u``\\ 、\\ ``v``\\ 、\\ ``gradu``\\ 、\\ ``gradv``\\ 、\\ ``x``\\ 、\\ "
"``gradx``\\ ），外加任何你打算通过 ``point_data``\\ 、\\ ``element_data``\\ 、\\ "
"``scalar_data`` 传入的键。以正确的阶数返回单点被积函数：标量问题返回 ``[B, B]``\\ （Element）或 ``[B]``\\"
" （Node / Facet）；分块问题返回 ``[B, B, H, H]`` 或 ``[B, H]``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:758 52b3443e468d4da3bbcffe9b92808f47
msgid ""
"**3. Stash parameters in ``__post_init__``**, not ``__init__``. The base "
"class's ``__init__`` wires up the projector, transformation, and edges; "
"``__post_init__`` runs immediately after with the constructor kwargs and is "
"where ``self.E = E`` belongs."
msgstr ""
"**3. 把参数存放在 ``__post_init__`` 中**\\ ，而非 ``__init__``\\ 。基类的 ``__init__`` "
"负责配置投影器、变换和边；\\ ``__post_init__`` 紧随其后运行，并接收构造函数的关键字参数，\\ ``self.E = E`` "
"这类语句就该写在这里。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:763 35ba9c7029e346a1b46d97277f80b559
msgid ""
"**4. Build the assembler via** "
":meth:`~tensormesh.ElementAssembler.from_mesh` **and call it.** Constructor "
"kwargs are forwarded to ``__post_init__``. The instance is callable (and is "
"an :class:`torch.nn.Module`, so ``.to(device)`` / ``.double()`` Just Work)."
msgstr ""
"**4. 通过** :meth:`~tensormesh.ElementAssembler.from_mesh` **构建装配器并调用它。** "
"构造函数的关键字参数会被转发给 ``__post_init__``\\ 。该实例是可调用的（并且是一个 "
":class:`torch.nn.Module`\\ ，因此 ``.to(device)`` / ``.double()`` 都能直接生效）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:768 a32718dd43a949cfb13e1b9de7395fb9
msgid "A self-contained template covering both styles:"
msgstr "一个涵盖两种写法的自包含模板："

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:792 4884a6afa30a429f9382e198c719dfec
msgid "**Debugging tips**"
msgstr "**调试技巧**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:794 a6eec341c5a948368aa33fcbfb22244b
msgid ""
"If the dispatch fails with ``ValueError: <name> is not supported``, the "
"parameter name doesn't match any built-in or any key you passed in the data "
"dicts. Check for typos like ``grad_u`` vs ``gradu`` or ``displacment`` vs "
"``displacement``."
msgstr ""
"如果分派失败并报 ``ValueError: <name> is not supported``\\ "
"，说明该参数名既不匹配任何内置名称，也不匹配你在数据字典中传入的任何键。请检查诸如 ``grad_u`` 与 ``gradu``\\ 、或 "
"``displacment`` 与 ``displacement`` 之类的拼写错误。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:798 634806ea544d468fb273acbaf5db0409
msgid ""
"If you hit a shape error inside ``forward``, set ``batch_size=1`` and call "
"the assembler on a one-element mesh; the tensors handed in are then small "
"enough to ``print`` and reason about. Remember that ``forward`` runs *under "
"vmap* — what you see has the leading element / quadrature dimensions "
"stripped."
msgstr ""
"如果你在 ``forward`` 内部遇到形状错误，请设置 ``batch_size=1`` "
"并在仅含一个单元的网格上调用装配器；这样传入的张量就足够小，便于 ``print`` 和分析。请记住 ``forward`` 是 *在 vmap 下* "
"运行的——你看到的张量已经去掉了前导的单元 / 求积点维度。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:803 b6e937fe417e42adbafccc77306ae25b
msgid ""
"For sanity-checking the assembled output, run a known integral: a "
"``MassElementAssembler`` should give ``1^T M 1 == area`` for the unit "
"function; a ``FacetAssembler`` returning ``v`` should sum to the boundary "
"length; a ``LaplaceElementAssembler`` applied to a linear field ``u = x`` "
"should yield zero residual. The ``tests/assemble/test_facet.py`` file has a "
"battery of these closed-form checks."
msgstr ""
"若要对装配输出做合理性检查，可以计算一个已知的积分：对于单位函数，\\ ``MassElementAssembler`` 应给出 ``1^T M 1 "
"== area``\\ ；返回 ``v`` 的 ``FacetAssembler`` 求和后应等于边界长度；作用于线性场 ``u = x`` 的 "
"``LaplaceElementAssembler`` 应给出零残差。\\ ``tests/assemble/test_facet.py`` "
"文件中就有一整套这样的闭式检查。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/forms.rst:811 bd55fd62a5644ed3a278a8f8f4b6b871
msgid ""
"For exhaustive examples covering hyperelasticity, plasticity, contact, and "
"fluid problems, see the :doc:`/example_gallery/index`."
msgstr "若需涵盖超弹性、塑性、接触和流体问题的详尽示例，请参见 :doc:`/example_gallery/index`\\ 。"

